content: Due to interstate operations, XPT services from Melbourne to Sydney will be replaced by a road coach service between Melbourne and Albury. urlText: Sydney To Melbourne XPT service alterations.
content: Due to interstate operations, XPT services to Melbourne will be a train service until Albury, with a road coach service on to Melbourne. Please contact 13 22 32 if you need to amend your booking. Entry to Victoria may require a Border Crossing Permit before you travel. Find out more and apply online: www.service.vic.gov.au/services/border-permit.
